"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13734/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13734/canvas/1/a24ab11d-9fe6-4379-b19c-acfb66898810","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:12:42.604Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds follows Alma down the stairs, reflecting how she now wields greater power in their relationship than before.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13734/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:991.1688311688313,183.89610389610382,345.97402597402606,686.4935064935066"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13734/canvas/1/3a33c4aa-39a4-4688-a765-f8a953e3e3c8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:13:30.287Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma is dressed exactly as she was for <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW132482573 BCX2\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-04031.html\"><u>the photoshoot</u></a> earlier in the movie, down to her hairstyle and earrings. Throughout their relationship, she has allowed Reynolds to shape her appearance, and this continues into their marriage. As she grows more involved in his life, she seems to adopt his lack of boundaries between work and personal life; in dressing herself for dinner, she makes herself almost a walking advertisement for his clothing.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13734/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:415.3246753246753,358.4415584415584,402.0779220779221,663.1168831168834"}}}]}]}]}